  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nHF1 introduces two changes to fork choice, as Vitalik has documented [here](https://notes.ethereum.org/@vbuterin/HF1_proposal#Proposed-fork-choice-changes-for-approximately-simultaneous-deployment-with-HF1):\r\n- Block/slot fork choice\r\n    - PR: https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2197\r\n    - [Paper](https://econcs.pku.edu.cn/wine2020/wine2020/Workshop/GTiB20_paper_8.pdf)\r\n-  Balance attack fix\r\n    - [Paper](https://arxiv.org/pdf/2009.04987.pdf)\r\n    - PR: https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2101\r\n    \r\nThese changes will require heavy-duty modification to our fork choice implementation. As the author, it seems sensible that I do it.",
